@startuml seq_21_manage_notifications
title Sequence Diagram: UC-21 Manage Notifications

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Notification Controller" as Controller
participant "Notification Service" as Service
participant "Notification Repo" as Repo

User -> Frontend: (1.1) Open Notifications
Frontend -> Controller: (1.2) GET /api/notifications
Controller -> Service: (2.1) Get User Notifications
Service -> Repo: (2.2) Fetch notifications for user
Repo --> Service: (2.3) List of Notifications
Service --> Controller: (3.1) Notifications data
Controller --> Frontend: (3.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> User: (3.3) Display notifications

User -> Frontend: (4.1/5.1) Mark as read / Delete
Frontend -> Controller: (4.2/5.2) PUT /api/notifications/{id}/read (or DELETE)
Controller -> Service: (6.1) Update Notification State
Service -> Repo: (6.2) Validate ownership
Repo --> Service: (6.3) Ownership confirmed

alt Mark as read
    Service -> Repo: (7.1) Update status to 'read'
    Repo --> Service: (7.2) Updated
else Delete
    Service -> Repo: (7.3) Delete notification record
    Repo --> Service: (7.4) Deleted
end

Service --> Controller: (8.1) Success
Controller --> Frontend: (8.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> User: (8.3) Update notification UI
@enduml
